text: Best pizza in town.  If you don't like it you picked everything on it so thats enough about that. Dine in  great pizza and reasonably priced .

text: Tables were separated for social distancing, which was awesome. I had not been out to eat in awhile, so that was nice to see! MOD is not my favorite because the pizza is always floppy, but this time it was actually ok.

text: Stopped in here for an early lunch. I came in about 15 minutes before opening hours and was having trouble ordering over the phone. The young lady took care of making my pizza for me regardless of it being a little early and made a delicious pizza with everything I wanted!
